data.description: Welcome to this 2 year old home that is located in the highly sought after area of Pickerington, in the community of Longview Highland. Minutes away from shopping, dining, freeways, schools, hospitals, police and fire departments.Sitting on a corner lot with a large front porch, spacious 2 car attached garage, full basement ready to be finished with your personal touch, office/den, stainless steel appliances with granite countertops and plenty of cabinet space in the kitchen, fireplace in the great room, 4 spacious bedrooms, walk-in closets,  2.5 bathrooms, and a 2nd floor laundry.Immediate possession.
